verbose_text: Angiography of 32 hpf morphants indicated that both 2 ng of aMO-e2i2 (5/28, P < 0.0001) or bMO-e2i2 (9/28, P < 0.01) significantly perturbed the normal blood circulation compared to control morphants (15/18) (XREF_FIG E).
